1
00:00:36,180 --> 00:00:40,940
=Ancient Bracelet=

2
00:00:41,340 --> 00:00:44,380
=Episode 11=

3
00:00:44,420 --> 00:00:46,660
=He's Lost His Mind=

4
00:00:51,390 --> 00:00:52,230
Zhaoli,

5
00:00:53,920 --> 00:00:55,840
you came on to me first this time.

6
00:00:58,860 --> 00:01:02,210
笙ｪA weary bird sways the branches笙ｪ

7
00:01:04,140 --> 00:01:08,200
笙ｪMy heart feels a gentle bond笙ｪ

8
00:01:09,480 --> 00:01:11,880
笙ｪPetals fall before the courtyard笙ｪ

9
00:01:12,220 --> 00:01:14,880
笙ｪNew sprouts cover the ground笙ｪ

10
00:01:14,880 --> 00:01:18,530
笙ｪI can't tell what's real or false笙ｪ

11
00:01:20,250 --> 00:01:23,800
笙ｪYou lean close, speaking softly笙ｪ

12
00:01:25,550 --> 00:01:29,620
笙ｪYour gaze blooms with grace笙ｪ

13
00:01:30,870 --> 00:01:32,520
笙ｪAffection fills the air笙ｪ

14
00:01:32,520 --> 00:01:35,280
笙ｪLonging takes on a clearer form笙ｪ

15
00:01:35,280 --> 00:01:36,560
笙ｪHow I wish笙ｪ

16
00:01:36,560 --> 00:01:40,140
笙ｪTo stay in this fleeting moment笙ｪ

17
00:01:47,280 --> 00:01:48,920
(The Fire Phoenix.)

18
00:01:49,430 --> 00:01:51,070
(Wu Zhaoli is the Saintess.)

19
00:01:52,070 --> 00:01:53,790
What was meant to happen

20
00:01:54,760 --> 00:01:56,590
has happened at last.

21
00:02:04,040 --> 00:02:05,680
Your wounds have healed.

22
00:02:09,240 --> 00:02:10,310
Does it still hurt?

23
00:02:10,750 --> 00:02:11,590
No, it doesn't.

24
00:02:13,150 --> 00:02:14,080
My whole body

25
00:02:14,840 --> 00:02:16,560
just feels a bit sore.

26
00:02:31,800 --> 00:02:32,640
Zhaoli,

27
00:02:33,520 --> 00:02:35,240
do you truly have feelings

28
00:02:35,750 --> 00:02:37,800
for Ying Du?

29
00:02:41,630 --> 00:02:42,470
My heart

30
00:02:42,800 --> 00:02:44,630
indeed leans toward him.

31
00:02:47,280 --> 00:02:48,400
But Zhaoli,

32
00:02:48,960 --> 00:02:52,080
you two can never truly be together.

33
00:02:58,430 --> 00:02:59,270
Grandmother,

34
00:03:00,150 --> 00:03:01,630
what do you mean by that?

35
00:03:02,240 --> 00:03:03,080
Zhaoli,

36
00:03:03,470 --> 00:03:06,000
it's time you learned
the truth of your birth.

37
00:03:06,240 --> 00:03:08,080
You were never an orphan.

38
00:03:08,400 --> 00:03:10,680
Your mother was Goddess Xingyue.

39
00:03:11,120 --> 00:03:12,630
She fell into a love tribulation

40
00:03:12,710 --> 00:03:15,240
and was punished by fate,
with her soul scattered.

41
00:03:15,910 --> 00:03:17,240
And your power

42
00:03:17,310 --> 00:03:19,430
was sealed at birth.

43
00:03:19,560 --> 00:03:21,800
Now, your power has awakened,

44
00:03:22,030 --> 00:03:24,240
and you've become the Saintess.

45
00:03:29,910 --> 00:03:30,750
Grandmother,

46
00:03:31,030 --> 00:03:32,520
even if I am the Saintess,

47
00:03:33,030 --> 00:03:35,150
why can't I be with Ying Du?

48
00:03:37,800 --> 00:03:39,680
They say the Saintess is bound by fate,

49
00:03:39,680 --> 00:03:40,960
unable to feel love,

50
00:03:41,560 --> 00:03:43,800
or she'll face punishment.

51
00:03:44,630 --> 00:03:45,870
You two are trapped

52
00:03:45,870 --> 00:03:48,470
in a cycle of grudges and tangled fate.

53
00:03:48,840 --> 00:03:49,680
You're destined

54
00:03:49,680 --> 00:03:52,800
to meet as enemies, bound by hate.

55
00:04:02,630 --> 00:04:03,470
Grandmother,

56
00:04:03,870 --> 00:04:05,190
it's only a legend.

57
00:04:06,000 --> 00:04:07,560
No matter what my identity is,

58
00:04:08,120 --> 00:04:09,590
my bond with Ying Du

59
00:04:10,870 --> 00:04:12,240
will never change.

60
00:04:18,560 --> 00:04:20,240
Let's check out the shop up ahead.

61
00:04:20,800 --> 00:04:21,640
Alright.

62
00:04:21,800 --> 00:04:22,640
Let's go.

63
00:04:22,640 --> 00:04:24,480
(Oracle, Teahouse)

64
00:04:24,480 --> 00:04:26,070
(Why is Oracle not here?)

65
00:04:26,070 --> 00:04:27,010
Why is it raining again?

66
00:04:27,021 --> 00:04:27,790
Who knows?

67
00:04:28,390 --> 00:04:29,230
Zhaoli.

68
00:04:29,600 --> 00:04:30,440
Let's go home.

69
00:04:30,630 --> 00:04:31,470
Hurry up.

70
00:04:31,600 --> 00:04:33,270
It's not too late for you to know

71
00:04:33,430 --> 00:04:34,480
the grudge with Ying Du.

72
00:04:35,560 --> 00:04:36,510
Che, you...

73
00:04:36,510 --> 00:04:37,570
I can use the Bracelet too.

74
00:04:37,870 --> 00:04:40,056
If you wish to see your past
and present with Ying Du,

75
00:04:40,800 --> 00:04:41,720
I can help you.

76
00:04:59,160 --> 00:05:01,070
You caused the fall of my entire tribe.

77
00:05:04,190 --> 00:05:05,030
Zhaoli.

78
00:05:06,070 --> 00:05:08,390
In your past life, Ying Du killed

79
00:05:08,479 --> 00:05:09,613
all your dear family and kin

80
00:05:09,630 --> 00:05:11,390
without exception.

81
00:05:12,270 --> 00:05:13,240
Not only that,

82
00:05:13,950 --> 00:05:16,310
you'll one day turn blades
on each other.

83
00:05:20,430 --> 00:05:21,560
But I have no memories

84
00:05:21,680 --> 00:05:23,240
of the dearest ones

85
00:05:23,720 --> 00:05:25,310
you speak of.

86
00:05:25,510 --> 00:05:26,630
I don't even know them.

87
00:05:27,260 --> 00:05:28,386
What about your grandmother?

88
00:05:28,950 --> 00:05:30,176
In the foretelling dream I had,

89
00:05:30,600 --> 00:05:31,950
Ying Du would kill her as well.

90
00:05:32,305 --> 00:05:33,272
If that's the punishment

91
00:05:33,283 --> 00:05:34,276
the Saintess will face...

92
00:05:34,287 --> 00:05:35,070
Enough, Che.

93
00:05:35,420 --> 00:05:36,440
Stop trying to sow discord

94
00:05:36,451 --> 00:05:37,680
between Ying Du and me.

95
00:05:38,040 --> 00:05:39,360
I don't believe any of this.

96
00:05:40,160 --> 00:05:41,000
Right now,

97
00:05:42,310 --> 00:05:44,000
I truly and deeply love him,

98
00:05:44,360 --> 00:05:46,120
and he has me in his heart too.

99
00:05:46,950 --> 00:05:47,870
That is enough.

100
00:05:48,510 --> 00:05:50,800
As for the punishment you speak of,

101
00:05:51,510 --> 00:05:53,000
I will face it together with him.

102
00:05:53,950 --> 00:05:55,240
You need not worry about it.

103
00:05:59,040 --> 00:05:59,880
(Zhaoli,)

104
00:06:00,380 --> 00:06:01,500
(I've failed time and again)

105
00:06:02,310 --> 00:06:04,360
(to kill Ying Du because of you.)

106
00:06:04,950 --> 00:06:05,800
(This time,)

107
00:06:06,430 --> 00:06:08,190
(I'll use your hand)

108
00:06:08,680 --> 00:06:10,240
(to rid him once and for all.)

109
00:06:16,680 --> 00:06:18,800
Help! Help me!

110
00:06:19,120 --> 00:06:19,960
Please spare me.

111
00:06:20,120 --> 00:06:21,000
(Something's wrong.)

112
00:06:21,000 --> 00:06:21,840
Spare me.

113
00:06:23,310 --> 00:06:24,270
Please spare me.

114
00:06:38,160 --> 00:06:39,070
Grandmother.

115
00:06:40,430 --> 00:06:41,270
Grandmother!

116
00:06:41,600 --> 00:06:42,440
Grandmother!

117
00:06:43,190 --> 00:06:44,030
Help me.

118
00:06:46,750 --> 00:06:47,590
Wu Luoluo.

119
00:06:48,800 --> 00:06:49,640
Help me.

120
00:06:52,720 --> 00:06:53,560
Wu Luoluo,

121
00:06:54,120 --> 00:06:55,430
what on earth is happening?

122
00:06:57,270 --> 00:06:58,480
Ying Du has lost his mind.

123
00:06:59,120 --> 00:07:00,800
He wants to destroy us all.

124
00:07:02,160 --> 00:07:03,000
Ying Du?

125
00:07:04,680 --> 00:07:05,520
That's impossible.

126
00:07:06,630 --> 00:07:07,480
No, it can't be true.

127
00:07:07,600 --> 00:07:08,830
It's real,

128
00:07:08,830 --> 00:07:10,000
terribly real.

129
00:07:11,390 --> 00:07:12,910
Wu Luoluo... Wu Luoluo!

130
00:07:27,160 --> 00:07:28,000
Grandmother!

131
00:07:28,480 --> 00:07:29,560
Don't!

132
00:07:37,480 --> 00:07:38,560
Zhaoli,

133
00:07:40,040 --> 00:07:41,630
go...

134
00:08:00,240 --> 00:08:01,080
Grandmother,

135
00:08:01,390 --> 00:08:02,800
wake up!

136
00:08:04,240 --> 00:08:06,360
It's me, Zhaoli!

137
00:08:13,800 --> 00:08:14,950
Why...

138
00:08:16,870 --> 00:08:17,830
Why?

139
00:08:22,120 --> 00:08:22,960
Ying Du,

140
00:08:24,430 --> 00:08:25,800
it really was you.

141
00:08:27,560 --> 00:08:28,560
Why?

142
00:08:30,720 --> 00:08:32,510
Why would you do this?

143
00:08:36,860 --> 00:08:41,510
笙ｪSnow falls upon my brows,
blurring suddenly笙ｪ

144
00:08:43,340 --> 00:08:48,310
笙ｪMemories turn,
forgiving time after time笙ｪ

145
00:08:49,770 --> 00:08:53,050
笙ｪTears or snowflakes, sweet or bitter笙ｪ

146
00:08:53,050 --> 00:08:55,950
笙ｪHard to tell them apart笙ｪ

147
00:08:56,470 --> 00:09:01,760
笙ｪVowing to give you
three lifetimes' happiness笙ｪ

148
00:09:01,760 --> 00:09:05,460
笙ｪIn this life, I still run toward you笙ｪ

149
00:09:05,810 --> 00:09:08,160
笙ｪNo matter the homeward journey笙ｪ

150
00:09:08,160 --> 00:09:12,200
笙ｪFalling to the deepest place
in your heart笙ｪ

151
00:09:12,200 --> 00:09:14,580
笙ｪAnd that is enough笙ｪ

152
