笙ｪAhead lies a path without snow or wind笙ｪ

153
00:09:18,580 --> 00:09:21,340
笙ｪBegonia blooms across the branches笙ｪ

154
00:09:21,710 --> 00:09:27,460
笙ｪOne more glance
may let love stand still笙ｪ

